---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Starfall Flute — Wenji Makes" description="A Stardew Valley music magic mod with six melodies, story-based unlocks, and performed spells.">
  <div class="mod-header"><div class="container">
    <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:16px;"><span class="tag">Music</span><span class="tag">Story</span><span class="tag">Magic</span></div>
    <h1>Starfall Flute</h1><p class="meta">Stardew Valley · Mod ID: 49168</p>
  </div></div>
  <section class="mod-content container">
    <img src="/images/home/starfall-flute.webp" alt="Starfall Flute" class="mod-image-full" />
    <p><strong>Find the flute, learn six melodies through the world, then perform them as real in-game spells.</strong></p>
    <p>This isn’t a one-button utility item. Melodies come from a shop, limited-time letters, NPC stories, and secret rituals. Your character performs each tune with music, animation, and visual buildup before the effect resolves.</p>
    <p>Melody effects include:</p>
    <ul style="color:var(--text-muted);margin:12px 0 24px 20px;">
      <li>Watering crops</li><li>Accelerating growth</li><li>Controlling nearby monsters</li><li>Returning home</li><li>Calling down lightning</li><li>Additional progression-based magic</li>
    </ul>
    <div style="margin-top:40px;display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;"><a href="https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/49168" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">Download on Nexus Mods</a><a href="/en/mods" class="btn btn-outline">← Back to Mods</a></div>
  </section>
</Layout>
